## Completed Work This Session

### Project: pixo — All 12 phases (Tasks #740-751)
Pure Go image processing library replacing nfnt/resize (3,319 importers, archived) and disintegration/imaging (2,899 importers, dormant). Core package: resize (4 functions, 7 filters via x/image/draw), transform (8 functions), crop (3 functions), adjust (6 functions incl. HSL-based saturation/hue), effects (blur, sharpen, grayscale, invert, 3x3/5x5 convolution), compose (4 functions with alpha blending), histogram, I/O (Open/Save/Decode/Encode with EXIF auto-orientation, JPEG/PNG/GIF/BMP/TIFF/WebP). Two compat packages: compat/resize (nfnt/resize drop-in), compat/imaging (disintegration/imaging drop-in). Golden image tests, edge case tests, I/O round-trip tests. 15 benchmarks. Go 1.22+, single dep (golang.org/x/image v0.23.0). 87.6% coverage. CI green.

